OL,3,CBetter future possible for Scotland
OL,4,Caway from Westminster, John Swinney to
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FA better future for Scotland away from
OL,8,FWestminster's "broken" economic model
OL,9,Fis possible, John Swinney will say
OL,10,Ftoday.
OL,12,FThe First Minister will tell the SNP's
OL,13,Fpre-election conference in Edinburgh
OL,14,Fthat Westminster will never work for
OL,15,FScotland.
OL,17,FThe party leader will link the UK
OL,18,FGovernment's handling of the economy
OL,19,Fto the cost of living crisis.
OL,26,@pD@OOUpD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
