OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773464672
OL,3,CBetter future possible for Scotland
OL,4,Caway from Westminster, John Swinney to
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FHe is expected to say: "All across
OL,8,FScotland, the message is the same.
OL,9,FPeople struggling to put food on the
OL,10,Ftable or scared to put the heating on.
OL,12,F"Parents worried their kids will never
OL,13,Fbe able to afford the life they
OL,14,Fenjoyed.
OL,16,F"And people who have worked their
OL,17,Fwhole lives finding that their pension
OL,18,Fjust isn't enough.
OL,26,@oD@XOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773464672
OL,3,CBetter future possible for Scotland
OL,4,Caway from Westminster, John Swinney to
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"Quite simply, the Westminster
OL,8,Feconomic model is totally broken. It
OL,9,Fdoesn't generate enough money for
OL,10,Fpublic services for the people.
OL,12,F"And it looks the other way as the
OL,13,Fsuper-rich get richer. Westminster
OL,14,Fhasn't worked for Scotland,
OL,16,F"Westminster doesn't work for
OL,17,FScotland. Westminster will never work
OL,18,Ffor Scotland."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773464672
OL,3,CBetter future possible for Scotland
OL,4,Caway from Westminster, John Swinney to
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FMr Swinney will claim that Westminster
OL,8,F"wants you to believe that this is as
OL,9,Fgood as it gets", something he said
OL,10,Fthe SNP "will never accept".
OL,12,F"Because the good news is, a much
OL,13,Fbrighter future for Scotland is ours
OL,14,Fto build," he will add.
OL,16,F"To glimpse that future we only have
OL,17,Fto lift our heads and look to our
OL,18,Findependent neighbours.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@PO]rD@IOUrD@[O]tD@AOUvD@JO]xD@
OL,26,AAOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773464672
OL,3,CBetter future possible for Scotland
OL,4,Caway from Westminster, John Swinney to
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"All around us right now there are
OL,8,Fcountries, just like Scotland, showing
OL,9,Fus the way.
OL,11,F"Higher living standards. Less
OL,12,Finequality. Higher pensions. Less
OL,13,Fpoverty. More money for public
OL,14,Fservices.
OL,16,F"That is the standard to which
OL,17,FScotland should aspire. Scotland has
OL,18,Fmore than what it takes to match them.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773464672
OL,3,CBetter future possible for Scotland
OL,4,Caway from Westminster, John Swinney to
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"Our people are every bit as talented
OL,8,Fand we've got natural resources that
OL,9,Fmost could only dream of.
OL,11,F"The fresh start that Scotland needs
OL,12,Fis within our grasp because at this
OL,13,Felection, we are not just in it to win
OL,14,Fgovernment.
OL,16,F"We're in it to win independence for
OL,17,FScotland."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOUyD@JO]
